data.description: **OPEN HOUSE SUN. 1/7 - 2 TO 4 PM** New Year, New Home! Welcome to your dream home in Deerfield! This charming two-story residence, nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, is now available for sale. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the warm and inviting atmosphere of the main floor. Enjoy a spacious and open living room with tons of natural light, a cozy fireplace with built-ins on either side of fireplace, and hard wood floors. The well designed kitchen features a secondary fireplace in the breakfast nook, creating a cozy atmosphere. The principal bedroom, conveniently located on this level, is a haven of relaxation. The ensuite bathroom features a whirlpool bathtub, separate shower, and dual vanities. Upstairs features a multi-purpose loft and two large bedrooms and secondary bathroom. Step outside to the meticulously landscaped backyard, where you can unwind in the fresh air or entertain friends and family on the patio. The property offers a perfect balance of greenery, matured trees and space for outdoor activities. Sellers are offering to cover a 2-1 buydown with asking price and accepted offer.
